            <run>User Conversion Rate for each Channel1.  The marks are labeled by User Conversion Rate and distinct count of User ID1. The data is filtered on Is First Touch and Campaign. The Is First Touch filter keeps 1. The Campaign filter keeps 6 of 6 members.
</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Observed user conversion rate by first-touch channel (user-level).</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Labels show conversion rate and distinct users (n).</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Filters: </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Is First Touch = 1</run>
