    <dashboard name='Multi-Touch Attribution Story' type='storyboard'>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='951' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98120' id='11' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99034' x='483' y='940'>
            <zone h='5875' id='12' type-v2='title' w='99034' x='483' y='940'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='92245' id='9' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99034' x='483' y='6815'>
              <zone h='92245' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99034' x='483' y='6815'>
                <zone fixed-size='140' h='16451' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='99034' x='483' y='6815' />
                <zone h='75794' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='99034' x='483' y='23266'>
                  <flipboard active-id='5' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                    <story-points>
                      <story-point caption='1. Goal and Baseline&#10;Goal: Identify which marketing channels and touchpoint sequences are associated with higher observed user conversion probability.&#10;Baseline: Overall user conversion rate is 83.6% in this dataset (user-level: at least one conversion event per user).&#10;Use the Campaign filter to compare results across promotions.' captured-sheet='Channel Overview' id='1' />
                      <story-point caption='2. First-touch channel insight&#10;First-touch view: The chart shows a narrow spread of observed conversion rates across channels.&#10;The n labels indicate results are based on substantial user counts, reducing small-sample noise.&#10;Interpretation is descriptive (association, not causation).' captured-sheet='Channel Overview' id='2' />
                      <story-point caption='3. Last-touch channel insight&#10;Last-touch view: The chart shows a similarly narrow spread of observed conversion rates across channels.&#10;This suggests single-channel attribution may not separate performance strongly in this dataset; sequence patterns can provide clearer differentiation.&#10;Next, we evaluate journey length and high-performing paths.' captured-sheet='Channel Overview' id='3' />
                      <story-point caption='4. Journey length and conversion pattern&#10;Journey length: Observed conversion rate increases with journey length in this dataset; however this may reflect selection effects (users who stay longer differ systematically) and the definition of conversion at user-level.' captured-sheet='Journey &amp; Sequences' id='4' />
                      <story-point caption='5. High-performing sequences and actions&#10;Top paths: Certain sequences show meaningfully higher observed conversion rates.&#10;To reduce small-sample bias, paths are filtered using Users in Path ≥ 20.&#10;&#10;Decision rule (matrix):&#10;High conversion + high volume: prioritize/scale&#10;High conversion + low volume: test and validate&#10;Low conversion + high volume: optimize or reconsider investment&#10;&#10;Any “prioritize/scale” action should be validated (e.g., A/B tests or incrementality checks) before budget reallocation.' captured-sheet='Journey &amp; Sequences' id='5' />
                    </story-points>
                  </flipboard>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{B6ED4218-9BFB-4111-B355-4A0E8B82CF93}' />
    </dashboard>
  </dashboards>
